    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream. This car has been babied since the day I got it\u2014honestly, it still has that fresh, new-car feel and looks absolutely flawless inside and out. It\u2019s been kept in a garage and treated with so much love, so it's in truly pristine shape. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new and ready for some adventures, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
