    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an uncompromising example of the E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit remains in concours-level condition, exhibiting zero parasitic draw or fluid seepage. The high-revving powerplant delivers linear torque through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes treated rod bearings and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and VANOS system operate within factory tolerances. The chassis retains its original torsional rigidity, complemented by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and staggered forged alloys wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber. Inside, the Novillo leather is supple with no bolster wear, and the dashboard remains free of UV degradation. This is a collector-grade specimen for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
