      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept, smoke-free, and spotless inside and out. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feel without the 'brand new' price tag, you\u2019ve found it. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I know you\u2019re going to love it as much as I do. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
